An absolute hard court classic, the adidas Barricade 6.0 shoe is a best selling, highest performance tennis shoe ever created world over. Complete with comfort features, the Adidas Barricade 6.0 version of tennis shoes are engineered with a Torsion System in the midfoot, ensuring absolute motion control during both, linear and lateral movement. Torsionability is the foot’s ability to adapt to any surface, without forcing the rearfoot to excessively move and stress itself out. The Adidas Torsion System, therefore, protects the feet from injuries, providing that much-required comfort and support especially when playing tennis on hard courts.

For the hard players
